quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  3,71,“Imi vanhu vakapihwa Gwaro (maJudha nemaKristu)! Sei muchisanganisa chokwadi nemanyepo uye muchiviga chokwadi muchiziva?”
  3,72,"Uye rimwe boka revanhu vakapihwa Gwaro rinoti: “Tendai mune izvo zvakadzikiswa kuvatendi (maMuslim) mangwanani uye moramba kupera kwezuva kuti vafuratire.”"
  3,73,"“Uye musava munotenda upi zvake kusara kweuyo anotevera chitendero chenyu.” Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Zvirokwazvo, gwara rechokwadi igwara raAllah” uye musava munotenda kuti wese anogona kuwana zvakafanana nezvamakawana, pamwewo vangapokane nemi pamberi paTenzi venyu. Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Makomborero ese ari mumaoko aAllah, vanopa kune wavanoda. Uye Allah vanogutsa (vakazvikwanira) zvisikwa zvavo, vanoziva zvakanyanya.”"
  3,74,"Vanosarudza kupa tsitsi dzavo (Islaam neQur’aan nehuporofita) uyo wavanoda, uye Allah ndivo muridzi wemakomborero akawanda"
  3,75,"Pakati pevanhu veGwaro (maJudha nemaKristu) pane uyo, ukamuchengetesa Qintaar (hupfumi hwakawandisa), anohudzosera kwauri; uye pakati pavo pane uyo, ukamuchengetesa Diinaar (Ndarama 4.25g) haaidzoseri kwauri kunze kwekuti wamira-mira uchisheedzera, nekuti vanoti: “Hapana chakaipa patiri nekutora midziyo yevasina ruzivo (maArabhu).” Asi vanotaura manyepo pamusoro paAllah vachiziva"
  3,76,"Chokwadi, wese anozadzikisa chibvumirano chake uye anotya Allah zvakanyanya, zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoda Al-Muttaqoon (vanoita mabasa akanaka, vatsvene)"
  3,77,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotenga nechitsidzo chaAllah nemhiko dzavo hupfumi hushoma, vachave vanoshaiwa chidimbu (chikamu chakanaka) mune ramangwana (Paradhiso). Allah havazombotauri navo kana kuvatarisa pazuva rekumutswa, kana kuvachenura, uye vachave vanowana mutongo unorwadza zvikuru"